2026-07-17 | Attempt to force a REAL per-rule timeout (xor AC-heavy rules)
  slow_xor 8-var In(h(a1 XOR..a8)): "Derivation checks ended" prints FAST; the hang is LATER
     precomputation, not the deriv check. slow5 with --saturation=1 --open-chains=1 completes
